edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.core

Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umn.cs.spatialHadoop.core.Rectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shape, TextSerializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Rectangle>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<Rectangle>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CellInfo, GridInfo, NASADataset, NASARectangle, SpatialAlgorithms.RectangleID

    public class Rectangle
extends Object
implements Shape, org.apache.hadoop.io.WritableComparable<Rectangle>
    A class that holds coordinates of a rectangle. For predicate test functions (e.g. intersection), the rectangle is considered open-ended. This means that the right and top edge are outside the rectangle.
    Author:
    Ahmed Eldawy
